-- Author Wolff Says Murdoch Most Close the New York Post (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-10T14:49:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-10/author-wolff-says-murdoch-most-close-the-new-york-post-audio-.html
Michael Wolff, author of the Rupert 
Murdoch biography "The Man Who Owns the News," says Murdoch has 
to get rid of the New York Post. Wolff talks with Bloomberg's 
Tom Keene, Scarlet Fu and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance." They are joined by  Brad Adgate  of 
Horizon Media.      (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:03
 